title: Prime Minister of Ukraine - Wikipedia
snippet: Yulia Svyrydenko is the current prime minister of Ukraine since 17 July 2025.

title: Yulia Svyrydenko - Wikipedia
snippet: Yulia Anatoliivna Svyrydenko (Ukrainian: Юлія Анатоліївна Свириденко, IPA: [ˈjul⁽ʲ⁾ijɐ ɐnɐˈtɔl⁽ʲ⁾ijiu̯nɐ swɪrɪˈdɛnko]; born 25 December 1985) is a Ukrainian politician who has served as the 19th prime minister of Ukraine since 17 July 2025.
